title: Fair Trade Cafe - Roosevelt
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Fair trade coffee and juice bar behind Trinity Cathedral. Has vegan lunch food like a hummus sandwich, salads, and weekly special; plus a few vegan baked goods like brownies and cookies. Some items can be made vegan by excluding cheese. Brunch on Sunday. Free Wi-Fi.
